{
  "texts": [
    "Among these images, 421,916 (64.5%, with 6312 reports) were for training, 76,900 (11.8%, with 1052 reports) were for validation, and 155,527 (23.8%, with 2028 reports) were for testing.",
    "The age of the participants had a median value of 51 years, with an interquartile range of 36 to 62 years.",
    "Of the participants, 5190 (55.3%) were male.",
    "More detailed characteristics of the dataset can be found in Table 1.",
    "The eye conditions extracted from the original FFA reports encompassed a wide range of conditions commonly encountered in clinical practice."
  ]
}